My first map, final release. my last version had a lot of bugs, but i have all of them fixed.
6 bugs were fixed, plus three traps added.
this is a medium sized map.
i find i fairly difficult, and i had it running on a server, and most said it was fairly difficult.
yes i know not alot of textures are used, but its better than the maps that are all orange/gray at least.
